Creating a Sales Insight Dashboard using Python (for data processing and exploratory visualizations) and Power BI (for interactive visualizations) involves a combination of:

Smart chart selection for clarity

Data storytelling

Interactive design elements in Power BI

Clean and aesthetic visual layouts

 Step-by-Step Plan for Building a Sales Insight Dashboard
1. Identify Key Metrics and Data Dimensions
Metrics (KPIs):

Total Sales

Sales by Region/Product

Sales Growth (%)

Average Order Value

Customer Acquisition & Retention

Dimensions:

Time (monthly/quarterly/yearly)

Product Categories

Sales Regions/Stores

Customer Segments
